# PocketBase API host for the client (rsbuild exposes PUBLIC_-prefixed vars to the app
# as import.meta.env.PUBLIC_PB_URL - see src/lib/pb.ts, SPEC 1). Copy to .env.local
# (gitignored) to override; do NOT commit real credentials or hosts.
#
# Resolution when PUBLIC_PB_URL is unset (ruling R11 - app code NEVER reads window.location;
# the HOST PAGE passes the origin into the app via Lynx globalProps.pbUrl):
#   - web dev   -> http://127.0.0.1:8090 (import.meta.env.DEV)
#   - web prod  -> the host page passes same-origin via globalProps.pbUrl (8.1's pb_public
#                  host; the Docker image serves the app from PocketBase, so same-origin)
#   - native    -> REQUIRED; a native host must set PUBLIC_PB_URL (or pass globalProps.pbUrl).
#
# e2e (unit 1.5) sets this to the disposable PocketBase, e.g.:
# PUBLIC_PB_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8091
